# currentItemIdentifier

**Instance Property**

An identifier of the current item.

## Declaration

```swift
var currentItemIdentifier: String? { get }
```

## Discussion

The coordinator sets this value in a previous call to [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVDelegatingPlaybackCoordinator/transitionToItem(withIdentifier:proposingInitialTimingBasedOn:)].
